<i>noun</i>: 탕진 [탕ː진], 분탕질 [분탕질] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>탕진 [탕ː진]</dt><br>
<dd>1. squandering; running through; wasting</dd><br>
<dd>재물을 다 써서 없앰.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of wasting one's property by using all of it.</dd><br>
<dd>2. wasting; using up; burning out</dd><br>
<dd>시간, 힘, 정열 등을 다 써 버림.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of consuming all of one's time, energy, passion, etc.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>분탕질 [분탕질]</dt><br>
<dd>1. squandering; dissipating</dd><br>
<dd>집안의 재산을 모두 없애 버리는 것.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of wastefully spending all of a household's wealth.</dd><br>
<dd>2. disturbance; commotion</dd><br>
<dd>시끄럽게 떠들며 소동을 일으키는 짓.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of causing a loud, noisy commotion.</dd><br>
<dd>3. robbery</dd><br>
<dd>(비유적으로) 쳐들어가서 재물을 빼앗거나 훔치는 짓.</dd><br>
<dd>(figurative) The act of invading and taking or stealing others' property.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>